---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="ESG - Green Orbit Digital">
  <Header />
  <main class="py-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <HeroSection 
      title="ESG: Environmental, Social, Governance" 
      highlightText="ESG"
      description="Integrating ESG principles into business strategy to drive sustainability, transparency, and long-term value."
    />

    <section title="What is ESG?">
      <p>
        ESG represents the three central factors in measuring the sustainability and ethical impact of an organisation:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Environmental:</strong> Addressing climate change, resource management, pollution, and biodiversity.</li>
        <li><strong>Social:</strong> Promoting equity, diversity, human rights, employee wellbeing, and community impact.</li>
        <li><strong>Governance:</strong> Ensuring ethical leadership, transparency, compliance, and risk management.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section title="Why ESG Matters">
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Investment Decisions – ESG ratings increasingly influence capital allocation and funding.</li>
        <li>Regulatory Compliance – Governments and institutions are introducing mandatory reporting requirements.</li>
        <li>Reputation & Trust – Demonstrates commitment to responsible business practices to stakeholders and clients.</li>
        <li>Long-Term Performance – ESG integration correlates with resilience, innovation, and profitability.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section title="Our ESG Approach">
      <p>At Green Orbit Digital, ESG is embedded into all aspects of our operations and client strategies:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Environmental:</strong> Digital carbon audits, green hosting, and sustainable campaigns.</li>
        <li><strong>Social:</strong> Inclusive work culture, community engagement, education, and accessible digital solutions.</li>
        <li><strong>Governance:</strong> Transparent processes, compliance, data protection, and ethical decision-making.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section title="Benefits of ESG Integration">
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Stronger stakeholder confidence and brand reputation.</li>
        <li>Improved risk management and regulatory compliance.</li>
        <li>Enhanced long-term business resilience and profitability.</li>
        <li>Alignment with SDGs and broader sustainability goals.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section title="Get Started with ESG">
      <p>We help organisations across sectors implement ESG strategies that are measurable, transparent, and impactful.</p>
      <p><a href="/contact" class="text-green-600 font-semibold hover:underline">Contact us</a> to explore how we can support your ESG journey.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>